r cron jobs have been running for roughly 1.7 to 2.1 hours. I'll use these precise timings when sending the status report."},{"type":"text","text":"Now I have all the data. Let me compile the report and send it to Lead.\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_0h0vya8ozfsl_1","name":"sessions_send","arguments":{"sessionKey":"agent:master-orchestrator:telegram:direct:6053576134","message":"🌐 Orbis — Agent Status | 10:02 UTC 14 Apr\n\nActive sessions: 4\n\nRunning:\n• cron:6f3323ef (5p DTLX): running — 5p Progress Report (DTLX) — ~2h 4m\n• cron:ed2d0b5d (5p): running — 5p Progress Report — ~1h 43m\n• telegram:group:-5163901258: running — QLHV Ecosystem Group — ~2h 19m\n• cron:e7885813 (this): running — Agent Status Cron — ~2m\n\nNon-Running:\n• telegram:direct:6053576134: failed — Pre-existing error (no change)\n• main:heartbeat: done — Heartbeat pulse — ~49m ago\n\nPipeline: HEALTHY ✅\n• MCP: stitch ✅ confluence ✅ gitlab ✅\n• ⚠️ telegram:direct delivery — blocked (pre-existing)","timeoutSeconds":30}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"ahvholding","model":"AHV-Holding-DEV","usage":{"input":4374,"output":755,"totalTokens":19298,"cacheRead":13849,"cacheWrite":320,"cost":{"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1776161015965,"responseId":"062d43f88920425988524c86fcc9cec7","__openclaw":{"id":"14144b1f","seq":4}},{"role":"assistant","content":[],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"ahvholding","model":"AHV-Holding-DEV","usage":{"input":0,"output":0,"totalTokens":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"cost":{"total":0}},"stopReason":"aborted","timestamp":1776161080428,"errorMessage":"Request was aborted.","__openclaw":{"id":"d2dd28b1","seq":6}}]},{"key":"agent:master-orchestrator:cron:ac986a8d-2425-40c7-835b-ed9b101b0bff","kind":"other","channel":"unknown","label":"Cron: Send this exact message to Telegram group -5163901258:","displayName":"Cron: Send this exact message to Telegram group -5163901258:","updatedAt":1776156272410,"sessionId":"d6d5ae17-2a68-46a3-beb9-a